---
title: Mediterranean Salmon Bulgur with Chickpeas, Zucchini & Grape Tomatoes
description: You haven’t tasted chickpeas until you’ve tried them roasted. Deliciously crunchy and more than worth the time they spend in a hot oven. In this recipe, they’re roasted with smoked paprika and tossed with toasted bulgur, roasted zucchini and tomatoes, and feta cheese for a mishmash of savory Mediterranean flavors. You likely won’t have leftovers, but if you do, you’ll find the dish tastes even better the next day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63347cf9755dc4e3e00c10a4-b58a6f30.jpg
